Description: HitchHttp
        =========
        
        Mock HTTP server that logs all incoming messages to stdout as JSON for
        easy parsing by HitchServe_.
        
        Documentation
        =============
        
        See:
        
        * https://hitchtest.readthedocs.org/en/latest/plugins/hitchhttp.html
        
